"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">0</crm:P57_has_number_of_parts><betmas:hasLocus><betmas:Locus><betmas:locusFrom/></betmas:Locus></betmas:hasLocus></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet110/msitem/ms_i1.64"><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/msitem"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniCont"/><dcterms:hasPart rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1933Mashaf#Chapter63"/><crm:P57_has_number_of_parts rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer">0</crm:P57_has_number_of_parts><betmas:hasLocus><betmas:Locus><betmas:locusFrom/></betmas:Locus></betmas:hasLocus></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet110/colophon/coloph1"><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/Colophon"/><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by>፸፻ወ፸ወ፬ እምፍጥረተ፡ ዓለም፡ ዘከመ፡ ሐሳቦሙ፡ ለቅብጣዊያን፡ ወዮናናዊያን፡</crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by> ወበ፷፻ወ፮፻፵ወ፪፡ ዘከመ፡ ሐሳቦሙ፡ ለዕብራዊያን</crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by>ወበ፲፻ወ፰፻፺ወ፫፡ እምዓመተ፡ እስክንድር፡ ዮናናዊ</crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by> ወበ፲፻ወ፭፻፸ወ፬፡ እምዓመተ፡ ሥጋዌሁ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ መድኅነ፡ ዓለም፡</crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by> ወበ፲፻ወ፪፻፺ወ፰፡ እምዓመተ፡ ሰማዕታት፡ ንጹሓን</crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by>ወበ፱፻ወ፺፡ እምዓመተ፡ አጋር፡ እብናዊ፡</crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by>    ወበ፳፡ ዓመተ፡ መንግሥቱ፡ ለመፍቀሬ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ንጉሥነ፡ ሠርፀ፡ ድንግል፡
                        </crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by>ወበ፲ወ፭፡ ዓመተ፡ ሢመቱ፡ ለአብ፡ ክቡር፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ሊቀ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ ዘእለ፡ እስክንድርያ፡</crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by>ወበ፯፡ ዓመተ፡ ሢመቱ፡ ለአባ፡ ማርቆስ፡ ሙጥራም፡ ዘኢትዮጵያ፡</crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by> ፪፡ 
              ለመጋቢት፡ በሐሳብ፡ ፀሐያዊ።</crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by> ወአመ፡ ፳ወ፬፡ ለሳባጥ፡ ወርኀ፡ ፬፡ ነገድ፡ ዘውእቶሙ፡ ሮማዊያን፡ ወሥራዊያን፡
              ወአፍርንጅ፡ ወአርመን</crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by>ወአመ፡ ፫፡ ለመሀረም፡ ጥንተ፡ አውራኂሆሙ፡ ለዓረብ፡</crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><dc:relation rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8550sardaDe"/><dc:relation rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5709JohnXIV"/><dc:relation rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6775Marqos"/><dc:relation rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3175Constant"/><dc:relation rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11515Antiochus"/><dc:relation rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4374Gabreel"/><dc:relation rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8410Salikof"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet110/layout/layout1"><dcterms:isPartOf rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet110"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/layout"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://w3id.org/sdc/ontology#UniMeP"/></rdf:Description><rdf:Description rdf:about="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet110/hand/h1"><dcterms:isPartOf rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet110"/><rdf:type rdf:resource="https://betamasaheft.eu/hand"/><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P79_beginning_is_qualified_by rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">1500-01-01</crm:P79_beginning_is_qualified_by><crm:P80_end_is_qualified_by rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date">1599-01-01</crm:P80_end_is_qualified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P78_is_identified_by>1877</crm:P78_is_identified_by></crm:E52_Time-span></crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:P4_has_time_span><crm:E52_Time-span><crm:P79_beginning_is_qualified_by rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/